{"tid":862314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就算係黃毓民想同泛民合作都做唔到，就馮你地？","createTime":"2018-10-14T17:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T06:43:19.000Z","uid":49388,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cf68277d09657af9994687b0d8f658c430ae5d66","tid":862314,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"同泛民團結咪笑死人啦<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民就係一個好好嘅例子，人地就件事去討論有分歧就已經俾呢班惡棍搞足十年，同佢團結？幫黎智英含次撚或者黎生會考慮下既～<br />\n<br />\n泛民主師有錢有權有媒體，你呢D奀挑鬼命走埋佢必然當你獵物食埋你個位～<br />\n<br />\n所以咪話你哋蠢囉，走上人哋個台做乜野<br />\n<br />\n明知人哋地頭搶咪正常人都唔會對返你有善，更可況係泛民，再者台下班教徒懵撚要醒一早醒咗，仲要醒都唔係一時三刻醒到，咁你搶咪為乜？整難自己塊面搞到自己咁樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訓醒未？"},{"pid":"bac84d9aa6f7f3ac74129ad41346bcd745525810","tid":862314,"uid":49388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"柒下柒下"},{"pid":"cc2f12f97b83a1135d0a4e00ca032ffa1cc93992","tid":862314,"uid":202348,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"10年五區公投之後已經要睇清楚泛民係咩人啦"},{"pid":"072bcc8b95b17713feddbb372c4ff0f3709bcc4e","tid":862314,"uid":38666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"邊條仆街言要同泛民合作？<br />\n泛民一日唔死 香港死路一條"},{"pid":"3720118288c2e5ca8ce2c7ddc0950cbc8c2bced9","tid":862314,"uid":178291,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"又一件"},{"pid":"61495546082a3fed4122ed70bdd4261b531b30d5","tid":862314,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:24:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34682912b19355856e9e8311bfe366482a1fafa0","tid":862314,"uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3720118288c2e5ca8ce2c7ddc0950cbc8c2bced9","tid":862314,"uid":178291,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"又一件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a188d47feca6608c947110e40128b394ae890414","tid":862314,"uid":34884,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"馮檢基單野仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n13年都叫做過泛民飯盒會召集人<br />\n一唔聽肥佬黎講去面參選<br />\n即刻變鬼<br />\n<br />\n仲講啲咩當年主權移交馮檢基走去臨時立法會<br />\n同葉國華有咩關係乜乜柒柒<br />\n扮fd扮廿幾三十年一野就反你枱<br />\n<br />\n試問點同呢班偽君子合作？<br />\n人地依家唔搞你本土派同獨派係因為你依家冇威脅咋<br />\n你幾『溫和』都好<br />\n泛民一聲令下，獨派都即刻變晒鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90aa2aaf7413f97d4923405bf65918b3647fae8","tid":862314,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"各位其主je，狗主成日話泛民係肥佬黎走狗，佢又何嘗唔係西方晚報走狗？五十步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b867ae341af40982f49e39d5c672609ceb378075","tid":862314,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f90aa2aaf7413f97d4923405bf65918b3647fae8","tid":862314,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"各位其主je，狗主成日話泛民係肥佬黎走狗，佢又何嘗唔係西方晚報走狗？五十步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:17:44.000Z","msg":"稿費仲高過陶傑<br />\n唔知百份老闆馬先生係欣賞教主<br />\n定係表面上係稿費，實際上係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc54271474d4a4905a7ceac0f0c5d8b302f89bc","tid":862314,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b867ae341af40982f49e39d5c672609ceb378075","tid":862314,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f90aa2aaf7413f97d4923405bf65918b3647fae8","tid":862314,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"各位其主je，狗主成日話泛民係肥佬黎走狗，佢又何嘗唔係西方晚報走狗？五十步笑百步<img src=